    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Tabs or decorative objects attached to a chain or ring supporting one or more keys. In modern usage, it can refer to such tabs incorporating a small electronic device for locking and unlocking a vehicle or performing other tasks remotely.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
